      • tryWaitForIdleSync

        public boolean tryWaitForIdleSync(long timeoutMillis)
        Tries to wait for an idle state on the main thread on best-effort basis up to timeoutMillis. The main thread may not enter the idle state when animation is playing, for example, the ProgressBar.

      • tryRunOnMainSync

        public boolean tryRunOnMainSync(Runnable runnable,
                                long timeoutMillis)
        Tries to run runnable on the main thread on best-effort basis up to timeoutMillis. The runnable may never run, for example, in case that the main Looper has exited due to uncaught exception.
